com.whaleal.mars.core.query

类 Sort

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.whaleal.mars.core.query.Sort
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Streamable<Sort.Order>, Serializable, Iterable<Sort.Order>, Supplier<Stream<Sort.Order>>

    public class Sort
extends Object
implements Streamable<Sort.Order>, Serializable
    Sort option for queries. You have to provide at least a list of properties to sort for that must not include null or empty strings. The direction defaults to DEFAULT_DIRECTION.
    另请参阅:
    序列化表格
